\section[Overview]{Overview}

The real-time tracking system of the different couriers working for MedLabs in Amman will 
function as follows – these couriers’ main job is to deliver the different medical samples 
from MedLabs' branches to the main branch for further testing. A portion of these workers 
is also lab technicians who will be taking samples from the patients from their homes. 
The system will track all of their routes and display them on the admin's dashboard. 
This will allow the admins to allocate tasks to couriers as efficiently as possible. 
All of which will be achieved through the workers' application that will serve admins and 
couriers alike. MedLabs' patients will be able to fill request-forms for samples to be taken 
from home by a capable lab technician using the separate application developed for the patients. \\
