The website will be accessible and should also run effectively on any desktop or laptop with an active internet connection.

\subsection[The Tracking System]{The Tracking System} 
The hardware used in this project is an Arduino-based vehicle tracking system. Arduino is a single-board microcontroller that - in this case -  
uses a Global Positioning System (GPS), and a Global System for Mobile Communications (GSM) to achieve real-time tracking of any vehicle or object that bears and makes use of
a SIM card even if it's offline. The system will be assembled inside of the vehicle.
